inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let timeRange = 1d;
let samples = 1000000;
let pageDurationThreshold = 3600s;
let allEvents = union pageViews
| where timestamp > ago(timeRange);
let allInterestingEvents = allEvents;
let sampledSessions = materialize(allInterestingEvents
| summarize by session_Id
| sample samples
| summarize makelist(session_Id, samples));
let data = allInterestingEvents
| where session_Id in (sampledSessions)
| project session_Id, timestamp, name
| join kind= inner
(
    allEvents
    | where session_Id in (sampledSessions)
    | project session_Id, timestamp
)
on session_Id
| project session_Id, TimeDiff = timestamp  - timestamp1, name, timestamp
| where TimeDiff > 0s and TimeDiff <= pageDurationThreshold
| summarize SecondsSpentOnPage = min(TimeDiff) / 1s by session_Id, name, timestamp;
data
| summarize Instances = count(), (Median, p75, p90) = percentiles(SecondsSpentOnPage, 50, 75, 90), Mean = avg(SecondsSpentOnPage) by name
| extend rank = 2, name = strcat('* ', name)
| union (data
| summarize Instances = count(), (Median, p75, p90) = percentiles(SecondsSpentOnPage, 50, 75, 90), Mean = avg(SecondsSpentOnPage)
| extend name = '* Overall', rank = 1)
| order by rank asc, Median desc
| project-away rank
| project ['Page Name'] = name, ['Sampled Page Views'] = Instances, ['Median (seconds)'] = round(Median, 1), ['75th Percentile (seconds)'] = round(p75, 1), ['90th Percentile (seconds)'] = round(p90, 1), ['Mean (seconds)'] = round(Mean, 1)

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let start = startofday(ago(1d));
union customEvents, pageViews
| where timestamp >= start
| where name in ('*') or ('*' in ('*')) or ('#' in ('*') and itemType == 'pageView') or ('&' in ('*') and itemType == 'customEvent')
| summarize Metric = dcount(session_Id) by bin(timestamp, 2h)
| extend Hour = hourofday(timestamp), WeekDay = dayofweek(timestamp)
| where 'No' == 'No' or (WeekDay != 0d and WeekDay != 6d)
| extend HourDisplay = case(Hour == 0, '12am', Hour < 12, strcat(Hour, 'am'), Hour == 12, '12pm', strcat(Hour - 12, 'pm'))
| extend Day = strcat(monthofyear(timestamp), '/', dayofmonth(timestamp), ' - ', case(WeekDay == 0d, 'Sun', WeekDay == 1d, 'Mon', WeekDay == 2d, 'Tue', WeekDay == 3d, 'Wed', WeekDay == 4d, 'Thu', WeekDay == 5d, 'Fri', 'Sat'))
| order by Hour asc
| extend Day1 = bin(timestamp, 1d)
| project-away timestamp, WeekDay, Hour
| serialize
| evaluate pivot(HourDisplay, sum(Metric))
| order by Day1 asc
| project-away Day1

inputs.name: Query
inputs.value:
let apdexThreshhold = toint('63');
let failureThreshhold = 1;
let apdexData = pageViews
| where timestamp > ago(1d)
| where name in ('*') or '*' in ('*')
| extend success = columnifexists('success', true)
| extend Failure = iff('ConsiderFailures' == 'ConsiderFailures' and success == false, 1, 0)
| extend InterestingDimension = iff(isempty(name)== true, 'Unknown', name)
| where InterestingDimension in ('*') or '*' in ('*')
| summarize AverageDuration = avg(duration), Failures = sum(Failure) by user_Id, bin(timestamp, 30m), InterestingDimension
| extend UserExperience = case(AverageDuration <= apdexThreshhold, 'Satisfied', AverageDuration <= 4 * apdexThreshhold, 'Tolerating', 'Frustrated')
| extend UserExperience = case(Failures >= failureThreshhold, "Frustrated", UserExperience)
| summarize Satisfied = countif(UserExperience == 'Satisfied'), Tolerating = countif(UserExperience == 'Tolerating'), Total = count() by timestamp, InterestingDimension
| project timestamp, ApdexScore = (Satisfied + (Tolerating / 2.0)) / Total, Users = Total, InterestingDimension;
let pageRelevance = apdexData
| summarize ["Apdex Score"] = avg(ApdexScore), Users=sum(Users) by InterestingDimension
| extend Relevance = iff(["Apdex Score"] == 0, 1.0 * Users * Users, Users / ["Apdex Score"])
| order by Relevance desc
| project InterestingDimension
| take 7;
apdexData
| join kind = leftouter (pageRelevance) on InterestingDimension
| extend InterestingDimension = iff(isempty(InterestingDimension1) == true, 'Other', InterestingDimension)
| project timestamp, ApdexScore, Users, InterestingDimension 
| summarize ApdexScore = avg(ApdexScore) by timestamp, InterestingDimension
| extend ApdexScore = round(ApdexScore, 3)
